[11/13/2025-13:48:12] [V] === Explanations of the performance metrics ===
[11/13/2025-13:48:12] [V] Total Host Walltime: the host walltime from when the first query (after warmups) is enqueued to when the last query is completed.
[11/13/2025-13:48:12] [V] GPU Compute Time: the GPU latency to execute the kernels for a query.
